Build a Docker container for the desi-outflows project.
=======================================================

```
docker build . -t desihub/nyxgalaxy
docker push desihub/nyxgalaxy:latest

docker tag desihub/nyxgalaxy:latest desihub/nyxgalaxy:v0.0.1
docker push desihub/nyxgalaxy:v0.0.1
```

To enter the container (with a shell prompt) on a laptop do:
```
docker pull desihub/nyxgalaxy:latest
docker run -it desihub/nyxgalaxy:latest
```

Or at NERSC:
```
shifterimg pull docker:desihub/nyxgalaxy:latest
shifter --image docker:desihub/nyxgalaxy:latest bash
```
